 Galvatron nodded. "Yes the old destrons were good soilders. But pick the 
ones from the predacons you feel would most benefit from thier change in 
ranks. But I dont want word of my liveing to be spread quite yet so refer to 
me as the dark one until I see fit." he sat back down in his command chair. 
"I have one person I want our side. We have the chamber of reconfiguration in 
this base thanks to guiledart. See if you can bring some of those preds here 
to talk...but only ones you think you may be able to covert to our side. I 
have a feeling our main enemy may be Megatron my formal self...and we'll need 
all the pred alliance we can get."

--part1_54.18e872f7.28a8bb77_boundary
